Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:47.43,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:55.46,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:03.64,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:09.16,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.54,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,projecting myself a little exaggeratedly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:19.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:25.25,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:31.85,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:39.88,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:44.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:51.16,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:58.63,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:06.66,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,before it all becomes a thing of the past
