Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Casebook of Sherlock Holmes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.19,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Konosu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:01.06,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stage left wing\N Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:23.08,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon helping Kaito-kun up, there is\Nblood on Sugimura's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:37.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.95,0:25:41.67,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:45.68,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:51.05,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our snooze-time date
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.27,0:26:11.27,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat of your budding warmth troubles me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.03,0:26:22.03,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how I feel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.41,0:26:28.89,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.92,0:26:34.31,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.34,0:26:40.02,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:45.03,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.06,0:26:47.99,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.02,0:26:51.74,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:55.79,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
